{"tid":2499104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸信會聯會會長羅慶才昨日以私人理由辭職，稱有機位帶愛犬一起到英國機會難得","createTime":"2021-04-21T15:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T15:44:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b99261dbdb2cc247ea7d6cd90b8a6834837472b","tid":2499104,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KX7rpgET2VDFJr4.JZ5leQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/nNfP_ocPDd3LFPY7orUD.A--~B/aD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/6882256e0f81166f87fe0a63efa6c27f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKX7rpgET2VDFJr4.JZ5leQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnNfP_ocPDd3LFPY7orUD.A--~B%2FaD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2F6882256e0f81166f87fe0a63efa6c27f&h=39a418a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】香港浸信會聯會會長羅慶才昨日以私人理由辭職，他曾發聲明促港府撤回逃犯條例、批評《港區國安法》。他接受傳媒查詢時，表示昨晚突有合適機位可以攜狗隻一同上機，因為不想錯過機會，所以急向浸聯會請辭。<br />\n<br />\n羅慶才原本任期尚有9日，但他昨日突然以私人理由請辭，他向傳媒表示，自己於年初已考慮退任，再加上不太接受到香港社會環境的轉變，於是決定退休移居英國。<br />\n<br />\n羅慶才稱，一直有留意飛往英國的航班，惟期間沒有可帶同狗隻的機位。直至昨晚有一班航班容許帶同狗隻，他於是與太太及狗隻一同飛往英國。羅慶才解釋指，這次機會十分難得，不想錯過，所以才會在上機前一分鐘才通知浸聯會，表示要辭職。<br />\n<br />\n而浸聯會稱表示，第一副會長林海盛牧師即日起署理會長職務直至4月30日。"},{"pid":"6aae75cce15797588c7874a69bd4c97fb7b99660","tid":2499104,"uid":56610,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"上機前一分鐘先辭職<br />\n仲要立即生效<br />\n睇黎佢都受左唔少氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf0e51c79d14feeb6bfb1cc823e07609139324e","tid":2499104,"uid":21962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6aae75cce15797588c7874a69bd4c97fb7b99660","tid":2499104,"uid":56610,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"上機前一分鐘先辭職<br />\n仲要立即生效<br />\n睇黎佢都受左唔少氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:30:17.000Z","msg":"點解有位帶狗仔咁正"},{"pid":"19fb215fb50125cae2e7c994529155a21d7c2f3d","tid":2499104,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"浸聯會班藍屍食住上"},{"pid":"0e244455dff6d9e2e76d30be0a91d920fefb85ad","tid":2499104,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"祝福，宜家呢個香港早走早着啦"},{"pid":"cba59a9fcb2988c68a11bb81bdf964b9200932c0","tid":2499104,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"祝佢平安健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄰國遲早拆香港教堂"},{"pid":"fc7afe47937985a8a154eb1601d69fea46736458","tid":2499104,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗仔搭飛機點計錢？"},{"pid":"ceefad108decdea8e09f5d28a0c34337fa5e650e","tid":2499104,"uid":141891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要帶埋狗仔走係好事"},{"pid":"213e26bf945d2be905e4918e381e4fab0270d850","tid":2499104,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"黎英國佈道都好 英國宗教線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}